      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，标题用\"Adding an item to the wishlist\"。第一阶段\"Enter online shop\"里面，用户需要先访问网站再登录对吧？登录步骤有什么特殊标记吗？",
